7- Rules that guide my life daily

Rule # 1
Live life on your terms.
This does not mean go through life with a my way or highway f*ck you attitude.
It’s simply means each day the goal is to live in your passion and purpose.
#mindsetcoach  #entrepenuer #womeninbusiness #dothework #21DaymindsetChallnge

Rule #2 Don't be afraid to fail.

YOU are afraid to fail because comfort is the human condition. Many don't take risks for fear of other people's opinions and how their efforts will be viewed. My words of wisdom ...Fvck them. 
Those who excel in life take calculated risks, win-lose, and learn. You can be like everyone else, play it safe, live a mundane life, or be an absolute savage and go after what you want.
Shift your mindset instead of saying “What if I lose or it doesn't work out?” Focus on what will happen when you WIN!
If for some reason it doesn't work out, and you’re not dead. Guess what? You get to fight another day and try again. Do not let your fear of failure keep you from living the life you truly deserve.
Do The Work 

#entrepernuer #mindsetcoach #lifecoach #motivationalspeaker #leadershiptraining

Rule #3 
Smile.😁Don’t Complain. No one cares.🤷🏽‍♀️

No one wants to hear your b*tching and moaning about how hard your life is and how terrible your day was.Either make changes or🤐. We all have a sob story no one cares🤷🏽‍♀️ Finding the good in a bad situation is life-changing🙌. Don’t believe me, try it for 30-days.
Remember nothing changes unless you do, nothing changes unless you do the work.
#mindsetcoach #entrepernuer #womeninbusiness #lifecoaching #dothework #speaker

Rule # 4 
How you do anything is how you do everything!
What you do when no one is watching is who your truly are. If you take short cuts , half ass approach to work, relationships , & life’s you will get half ass results. Take pride and have integrity in your work. The results will speak for themselves. 
-Do The Work 
#motivationalspeaker #mindsetcoaching #entrepreneurship #womeninbusiness

Rule #5 Do unto others as you would have them do unto you.
Treat people the was you want to be treated. I always say live your life in such a way that you can sleep good at night. 
You want kindness be kind. You want love be loving. You  want truth always be honest. If we did this all the time and not just sometimes imagine how amazing this world would be. 
#21daymindsetchallenge #entrepreneur #motivationalspeaker #lifecoach #mindsetcoaching

The Monday message is simple. “They don’t want you 🫵 to win. Win anyway ! “
Tag friend who needs to hear this. 
_______________________
#mondaymotivation #motivationalspeaker #mindsetcoach #entrepreneur

Rule # 6
Do not let other people project their insecurities on to you.

Do not let anyone put their worry doubt fears insecurities uncertainty on YOU! Just because they can’t and didn’t, does not mean you won’t. 

Remember it’s your job to believe in yourself when no one else will.
#mindsetcoach #speaker #rulesforlife 
#entreprenuer

Rule # 7 
It’s You vs. You 
The goal is to be better than the person in the mirror. If you wake up daily focusing on becoming your best self you will have no time to get distracted . Why ? You are too busy and preoccupied working on YOU!!

Imposter Syndrome is something many people struggle with as they pursue to attain their next level of growth - especially in business although it can apply to different areas of life.

Imposter syndrome is loosely defined as doubting your abilities and feeling like a fraud. It disproportionately affects high-achieving people, who find it difficult to accept their accomplishments. Many question whether they're deserving of accolades.

In order to break the cycle, the cycle MUST be broken in all or some aspects to break free of what is holding you back.
